" data-dictid=\"b10ce4acbf169277719323ffd12306\">node</span> (LN) regions on both sides of the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"5b42867b61169277718692205c2447\">diaphragm</span> are involved</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>IV</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Diffuse or <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"f4006059f916927771865569d4da7d\">disseminated</span> disease +/- LN involvement</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:NaN\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Low-risk disease</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>High-risk disease</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Stage I, II, IIIA</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Stage IIIB, IV</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Absence of B symptoms, no evidence of bulky disease</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Presence of B symptoms, bulky mediastinal/peripheral lymphadenopathy, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7fa42cc96416927771877d60e9fae2\">extranodal</span> extension</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Treatment: 2-4 cycles of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"8602c4b260169277718439bb122cb0\">chemotherapy</span> (ABVD regimen), low-dose field radiation</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Treatment: 4-6 cycles of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"8602c4b260169277718439bb122cb0\">chemotherapy</span> (ABVD) with/without radiotherapy.</p>\n<p>Hematopoietic stem cell transplant<strong> </strong>in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"b4b361c37616927771979541177070\">relapse</span> or in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3790c638ab16927771970a0a41d3ab\">refractory</span> cases.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
